      • saveFilter

        Ack saveFilter(ID branchId,
               boolean shared,
               java.lang.String name,
               java.lang.String type,
               com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.JsonNode parameters)
        Saves a filter for a branch. This method does nothing if the user is not logged, or if the filter type is not found, or if the parameters are not valid.
        Parameters:
        branchId - Branch to save the filter for
        shared - If the filter must be shared in the branch (needs specific authorisation)
        name - Name of the filter
        type - Type of the filter
        parameters - Parameters for the filter
